{
  "id": "69ef333e47169e9096b5793d",
  "title": "誤用としての提喩",
  "created": 1777283908,
  "updated": 1777301019,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69ef333e47169e9096b5793d",
      "text": "誤用としての提喩",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f42",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef337e0000000000725f73",
      "text": "ページ名は[atohs.icon]さんのコメントから",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283967,
      "updated": 1777283982
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33a90000000000725f74",
      "text": " [2026/04/27#69ef0dad00000000008fbdd3]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777284010,
      "updated": 1777284010
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef337d0000000000725f72",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283966,
      "updated": 1777283966
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f43",
      "text": "[誤用]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f44",
      "text": "[提喩]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef340e0000000000d38845",
      "text": "\t[シネクドキ]の日本語って提喩っていうのか[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777284111,
      "updated": 1777300142
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f48",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777284038
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f4d",
      "text": "団体の名前と団体の事業のそれを同一視する例",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f4e",
      "text": "　よくあるやつ",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f4f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f50",
      "text": "　[Internet Archive]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f51",
      "text": "　\t[Wayback Machine]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f52",
      "text": " \t\t上位区分は総合的なアーカイブサービス",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f53",
      "text": " \t\t下位区分はその事業の一環として行われるWeb魚拓サービス",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f54",
      "text": " Uber",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f55",
      "text": " \t[Uber Eats]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f56",
      "text": " \t\t上位区分は企業名",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f57",
      "text": " \t\t下位区分はその企業の出前サービス",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283927
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef335d0000000000725f70",
      "text": " [Wiki]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283934,
      "updated": 1777283939
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f58",
      "text": " \t[Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283940
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33640000000000725f71",
      "text": " \t\t[WikipediaをWikiって略すな！]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283941,
      "updated": 1777283948
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef74090000000000543dad",
      "text": " \tこれは略語の問題かなと思ったりもします[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777300489,
      "updated": 1777300496
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef74100000000000543dae",
      "text": " \t\t[USBメモリをUSBって略すな！]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777300496,
      "updated": 1777300506
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef741b0000000000543daf",
      "text": " \t\t[ギガバイトをギガって略すな！]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777300507,
      "updated": 1777300514
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef74230000000000543db0",
      "text": " \t\t[キログラムをキロって略すな！]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777300515,
      "updated": 1777300521
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef74290000000000543db1",
      "text": " \t\t[キロメートルをキロって略すな！]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777300522,
      "updated": 1777300537
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef74410000000000543db2",
      "text": " \t\t（略語の問題だと思うということは、略語のみの問題だと思うということを意味せず、略語と提喩の両方の問題だと思う、ということです）",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777300545,
      "updated": 1777300573
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f59",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f5a",
      "text": "最大手のブランド名がそのジャンル名を乗っ取る例",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777284171
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f5b",
      "text": "　[メガドライブを頑なにファミコンと呼ぶ母ちゃん]現象",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f5c",
      "text": "　前項の「団体の名前と団体の事業のそれを同一視する例」が業界の規模に拡大するとこうなる[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f5d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f5e",
      "text": " 音声合成ソフトウェア",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f5f",
      "text": " \t[Vocaloid]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f60",
      "text": " ビデオゲーム(機)　（特に家庭用）",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f61",
      "text": " \tファミコン",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f62",
      "text": " \t\tなおアメリカではセガ・ジェネシス含め「ニンテンドー」と呼ばれていた",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777284155
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f63",
      "text": " [ステープラー]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f64",
      "text": "　\t[ホッチキス]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777301019
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef75dc0000000000942f5e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777300957,
      "updated": 1777300978
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f65",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f66",
      "text": "関連？",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f67",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f68",
      "text": "上位区分から下位区分が忘れられると、この誤用の認識を持つ人も消え去る問題",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f69",
      "text": " 「最大手のブランド名がそのジャンル名を乗っ取る例」の類例か[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777284167
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f6a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f6b",
      "text": "　例えば「[アナログレコード]」という区分けから[SPレコード]が忘れられている",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f6c",
      "text": "　\tそのため、これを[アナログレコード]全てを「(塩化)ビニール」と言い換えてしまう事態が発生している",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f6d",
      "text": "　\t [SPレコード]を含めて[アナログレコード]について語るコミュニティが限られてしまう実害が発生している",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777284201
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33430000000000725f6f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777283908,
      "updated": 1777283908
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33cc0000000000725f7f",
      "text": "未分類",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777284045,
      "updated": 1777284052
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33cd0000000000725f80",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777284045,
      "updated": 1777284045
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33c90000000000725f79",
      "text": " [ピタゴラスイッチ]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777284042,
      "updated": 1777284043
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33ca0000000000725f7b",
      "text": " \t[ピタゴラ装置]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777284043,
      "updated": 1777284043
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33ca0000000000725f7c",
      "text": " \t\t上位区分は番組名",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777284043,
      "updated": 1777284043
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33ca0000000000725f7d",
      "text": " \t\t下位区分は番組内のコーナー",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777284043,
      "updated": 1777284043
    }
  ]
}